INSERT INTO goodreads VALUES(36642458,'Skyward (Skyward, #1)','Brandon Sanderson','Sanderson, Brandon','','=""','=""',4,4.5499999999999998223,'Gollancz','Hardcover',513,2018,2018,'','2018/12/10','Sanderson is pretty consistently good, across the wide range of worlds and genre''s and subgenre''s he writes in.  This one reminded me of quite a few other books in general plot/setting/characters so it''s not particularly original compared to some of his other stuff but that doesn''t make it any less enjoyable.  FTR, I read along with the audio book (at 1.5x speed), and the narrator isn''t bad.');
INSERT INTO goodreads VALUES(37640636,'Lies of the Beholder (Legion, #3)','Brandon Sanderson','Sanderson, Brandon','','="159606885X"','="9781596068858"',3,4.1100000000000003197,'Subterranean Press','Hardcover',148,2018,2018,'','2018/12/10','I read this is the "The Many Lives of Stephen Leeds".  It was ok but kind of a let down from the 2 previous stories and how his mysterious past and some plot elements "wrapped up".  This world and this character really could have supported 6 or more full length novels, or a dozen novellas like these, maybe some short stories about very brief cases too.  It''d make a great TV show too, though there''s already a "Legion".');
